  About SeaChange
  
  

SeaChange is an originator of content management, delivery and advertising software solutions that have shaped the premium video and advertising market for nearly 25 years.




		SeaChange provides on-premise and cloud-based solutions that enable the world’s foremost TV service providers and content owners to create millions of compelling, individualized consumer experiences on every device, every day, and dramatically accelerate revenue with targeted advertising, promotions and recommendation capabilities.

